wikipedia_page.main: Amin Mohammed (born 21 February 1996), known professionally as Chunkz, is an English YouTuber, host, entertainer and former musician. As of June 2021, his YouTube channel has over 1.8 million subscribers and 142 million video views. He is a member of the YouTube group Beta Squad.

Chicken Shop Date began as a humorous column written by Dimoldenberg for the youth magazine The Cut, which was based at the Stowe Centre, a youth club on Harrow Road, London. It was other members' interest in grime that led her to interview grime artists, as she "wanted to know more about the music"; she began by interviewing "friends of friends". Dimoldenberg had the idea to frame the interviews as dates, and the location of a chicken shop was chosen as it was "somewhere you wouldn’t usually go on a date". The first filmed episode was released in 2014 – it featured a "date" with the grime MC Ghetts. The show has since featured Sean Paul, Daniel Kaluuya, Dave, AJ Tracey, KSI, Chunkz, Aitch, ArrDee, Jack Harlow, Finneas, Ed Sheeran, Bimini Bon Boulash, Maya Jama, Jade Thirlwall and Big Narstie amongst others. The show has also featured footballers like Jesse Lingard, Bernardo Silva ,Tammy Abraham and John Stones.
